  Marked ~sparc (bug #328121)

  07 Aug 2010; Lennart Kolmodin <kolmodin@gentoo.org> arrows-0.4.2.0.ebuild:
  Remove the CABAL_FEATURES flag hscolour as it's not yet supported in
